sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI
    participant API
    participant Retriever
    participant LLM
    participant Guardrails
    participant Warehouse

    User->>UI: Enter question
    UI->>API: POST /query
    API->>Retriever: Fetch context
    Retriever-->>API: Metadata context
    API->>LLM: Generate SQL (question + context)
    LLM-->>API: SQL statement
    API->>Guardrails: Validate SQL
    Guardrails-->>API: valid/invalid
    alt valid and execute=true
        API->>Warehouse: Execute SQL
        Warehouse-->>API: Result set
    else not valid or execute=false
        API-->>API: Skip execution
    end
    API-->>UI: SQL + result + warnings
